<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.9.3">
<l>cuḷaikoṇṭa palaṅkaṉikaḷ tēṉpāya katalikaḷiṉ</l>
<l>tiḷaikoṇṭa paḻaṅkeḻumu tikaḻcōlait tirunaṟaiyūr</l>
<l>vaḷaikoṇṭa vaṇṇattaṉ piṉtōṉṟal mūvulakō</l>
<l>ṭaḷaiveṇṇe yuṇṭāṉta ṉaṭiyiṇaiyē yaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirunaṟaiyūr with glittering groves where banana fruits</l>
<l rend="indent">which crowd together</l>
<l>Are plentiful, while nectar flows from jackfruit with pulp,</l>
<l>O heart, take refuge at both feet of the one who ate churned butter,</l>
<l>Along with the three worlds, [in his] appearance</l>
<l rend="indent">after the one with the color of a conch.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
